Tamable and ridable bluebacks and redbacks!

Both bluebacks and redbacks can now be tamed and ridden like any other mount. In the wild they may spawn with a juvenile, which you can tame and raise like any other juveniles. When grown, it becomes a mount for you to place a saddle on and ride. You can use the Basic Riding Saddle for both.
Comes with an updated talent tree for the Blueback and a new talent tree for the Redback to level up your mounts. 

Largely inspired by JimK72's famous Bear Mount and JimK Workshop Pets, check out those as well! This mod is of course compatible with both, as well as my Buyable Zebras Mod.

